{"tid":2298217,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港電台：美退出開放天空條約　美俄關係雪上加霜","createTime":"2020-11-24T01:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T01:59:04.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a26b4914a23d9184b8a909fc2427586112847377","tid":2298217,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T01:59:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>美國國務院發表聲明，正式退出《開放天空條約》，條約容許簽署國之間可在彼此領空進行非武裝的空中偵察，被視為冷戰後建立軍事互信的重要條約。</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國批評俄羅斯未有遵守條約內容，留在條約對美國無益處。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>專家擔心美俄關係會雪上加霜</strong>，亦憂慮另一條在明年到期，更重要的軍控條約的前景。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561570-20201124.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561570-20201124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaP56hpy2SSQtx6ElJ%2BvIbMI%3D&h=3bd6960e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561570-20201124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ef8d264b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561570-20201124.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}